==English==

===Noun===
'''[[illative]] [[case]]'''

#{{grammar}}: [[case]] used to indicate movement '''into''' something; for example, ''into the house''. Some languages that make use of the illative are [[Finnish]], [[Hungarian]], and [[Quechua]].

